              <p>Use morning and night after cleansing and toning. Apply 2–3 drops to face and neck and gently press into the skin. Follow with moisturizer and use sunscreen during the day.</p>
            {%- elsif product.handle == 'anti-frizz-keratin-serum' or product.handle == 'anti-frizz-serum' or product.handle == 'keratin-serum' -%}
              <p>After washing or styling, take a small amount of Anti Frizz Keratin Serum and apply evenly through damp or dry hair, focusing on mid-lengths and ends. Avoid the roots and style as desired.</p>
