            {%- elsif is_hair_mist -%}
              <p>Mist evenly over dry or damp hair from 6-8 inches away. Use throughout the day as needed to refresh and scent your hair.</p>
            {%- elsif product.handle == 'centella-skin-toner-copy' or product.handle == 'renewal-cleanser' -%}
              <p>Use morning and night. Apply a small amount to wet skin and gently massage over face and neck. Rinse thoroughly with lukewarm water and follow with toner, serum, and moisturizer.</p>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="acc-item">
          <summary class="acc-summary">Elaris Tricks <span class="acc-icon">+</span></summary>
          <div class="acc-content">
            {%- if product.handle == 'night-cream' or product.handle == 'e7-korean-glass-skin-centella-night-cream-copy' -%}
              <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Apply a slightly thicker layer on dry areas to maximize overnight hydration</li>
                <li>Combine with your serum for enhanced repair benefits</li>
                <li>Use consistently to see a reduction in fine lines and dark spots</li>
              </ul>
            {%- elsif product.handle == 'tranexamic-serum' -%}
              <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Apply on slightly damp skin for better absorption</li>
                <li>Use consistently for visible brightening results</li>
                <li>Pair with sunscreen daily to prevent further discoloration</li>
                <li>Layer with moisturizer to lock in hydration</li>
              </ul>
            {%- elsif product.handle == 'anti-frizz-keratin-serum' or product.handle == 'anti-frizz-serum' or product.handle == 'keratin-serum' -%}
              <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Apply on slightly damp hair for better absorption and control</li>
                <li>Use a small amount to avoid product buildup</li>
                <li>Apply before heat styling for added protection</li>
                <li>Use on dry hair to tame flyaways instantly</li>
              </ul>
            {%- elsif is_centella_serum -%}
              <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Apply on damp skin to boost absorption and enhance glow</li>
                <li>Layer with a moisturizer to lock in active ingredients effectively</li>
                <li>Use day and night consistently for more visible tone correction</li>
                <li>Pair with sunscreen in the morning to protect brightening results</li>
              </ul>
            {%- elsif is_glutathione_cream -%}
              <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Apply on slightly damp skin for better absorption</li>
                <li>Use consistently for visible brightening results</li>
                <li>Pair with a serum to enhance results</li>
                <li>Use sunscreen daily to maintain an even tone</li>
                <li>Massage gently to boost skin absorption</li>
              </ul>
            {%- elsif is_hair_mist -%}
              <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Spray on your hairbrush before brushing for an even distribution</li>
                <li>Use after styling to add a final touch of shine and fragrance</li>
